00:14:32.550 --> 00:14:33.950
advantage of things on iOS 7.

00:14:34.290 --> 00:14:38.740
HomeSnap Real Estate, great app,
completely redesigned for iOS 7.

00:14:38.880 --> 00:14:40.810
Vimeo.

00:14:40.970 --> 00:14:47.360
Albumatic, NBC, Snap Guide, Open Table,
and then the Ted app.

00:14:47.640 --> 00:14:51.080
These are all fantastic
apps in and of themselves,

00:14:51.150 --> 00:14:55.620
and every one of these developers
took the time to do-- to make

00:14:55.780 --> 00:15:00.520
a huge effort and to clean up,
to change, to improve legibility,

00:15:00.660 --> 00:15:05.250
and to optimize their
UI for-- to fit in with iOS 7.

00:15:05.440 --> 00:15:08.860
So a real terrific job from
all of these developers.

00:15:09.260 --> 00:15:14.260
And so these are just, you know,
a small set of the hundreds of

00:15:14.320 --> 00:15:18.510
thousands of apps that are being updated
for iOS 7 every day and that have

00:15:18.510 --> 00:15:21.000
transitioned to the new UI for iOS 7.

